{"tid":1204708,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6月12日齊齊坐地鐵玩Pokemon Go捉水系精靈，精靈訓練員裝備&須知一覽","createTime":"2019-06-11T15:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T13:17:52.000Z","uid":109923,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5ef17427631d573164e4791646e1296a0fb36c76","tid":1204708,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:54:32.000Z","msg":"精靈訓練員裝備&amp;須知一覽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1,下載好Pokemon Go嘅手機，先啟動好方便隨時切換App<br />\n2,尿袋，玩手機當然要帶尿袋<br />\n3,請勿使用站內插座插電，會觸犯《盜竊罪條例》的「竊取電力」罪名，最高可被判監禁五年<br />\n4,港鐵站範圍內的公共廁所 (<a href=\"http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/services/nearbytoilet.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcustomer%2Fservices%2Fnearbytoilet.html&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiTnF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=dc180d7d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/services/nearbytoilet.html</a>)<br />\n5,帶好水樽，港鐵有飲水機，太子站近A出口、東涌站近D出口、荃灣站近C出口<br />\n6,可以帶定風扇、外套，萬一太多人太焗/冷氣太凍/港鐵熄冷氣<br />\n7,推薦捉精靈路線，港島線(上環至銅鑼灣)、荃灣線(過海)、東涌線(過海)、將軍澳綫(過海)，過海可以捉水系精靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8,尿袋、風扇、外套都幾多嘢，帶個喼就更方便<br />\n9,拖喼被職員或警察問可以講普通話，親，我是來香港購物的，不清楚地鐵怎麼坐，你能教我不？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10,千祈唔好擋住車門/閘門，閂極都閂唔到就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7c79356ef0b817fe489e600e3c06342f4aabce","tid":1204708,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T16:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf2268c42847d42df8a0254e000318638f856e2","tid":1204708,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}